 Author    : Derek Lane
 System    : LOGITECH MODULA-2/86

 Interactive control of the radar.  CompletePicture is
 TRUE if a complete picture was received from the radar.
 The parameters of the radar can be found by reading 
 RadarParams in module Control.

========================================================
*)

VAR
  CompletePicture : BOOLEAN;   (* TRUE if a complete picture was 
                                  received from radar. *)

PROCEDURE RadarInteract;
(* Interactive control of radar. *)

END Interact.
